b6cddf3a\"><p data-block-id=\"paragraph-ec8e2465-28b4-4cf4-a289-2e257def415b\" id=\"paragraph-ec8e2465-28b4-4cf4-a289-2e257def415b\">成熟的研发技术团队</p></li><li data-block-id=\"listitem-78a4111d-95d3-4c1b-a463-8ce387480c5a\" id=\"listitem-78a4111d-95d3-4c1b-a463-8ce387480c5a\"><p data-block-id=\"paragraph-844a9ba2-71d4-4522-8a83-8cec766f4b6b\" id=\"paragraph-844a9ba2-71d4-4522-8a83-8cec766f4b6b\">行业领先的品牌效应</p></li></ul></div></div><div data-block-id=\"localcolumnblock-02a31727-1698-495d-9698-18e6c9e41c54\" id=\"localcolumnblock-02a31727-1698-495d-9698-18e6c9e41c54\" data-width-ratio=\"50\" data-local-column=\"true\" class=\"feishu-columns-block__col-wrap\"><div class=\"feishu-columns-block__col\"><h3 data-block-id=\"heading-e5165de3-cf6a-43ab-b1b3-52c12981eb47\" id=\"heading-e5165de3-cf6a-43ab-b1b3-52c12981eb47\" data-heading-id=\"heading-e5165de3-cf6a-43ab-b1b3-52c12981eb47\">W (Weaknesses) 劣势</h3><ul><li data-block-id=\"listitem-779e8344-c0c2-43cd-bcf1-4190f41d855c\" id=\"listitem-779e8344-c0c2-43cd-bcf1-4190f41d855c\"><p data-block-id=\"paragraph-60c5a017-bd74-426c-847e-d08e85b51be1\" id=\"paragraph-60c5a017-bd74-426c-847e-d08e85b51be1\">产品推广渠道较为单一</p></li><li data-block-id=\"listitem-b78f7503-aa20-47f6-97f1-87e7789b8bed\" id=\"listitem-b78f7503-aa20-47f6-97f1-87e7789b8bed\"><p data-block-id=\"paragraph-0375b16e-6d6e-437d-bb5b-bdeeb59cf77c\" id=\"paragraph-0375b16e-6d6e-437d-bb5b-bdeeb59cf77c\">用户流失率略高于行业平均</p></li></ul></div></div></div><div data-local-block=\"columns\" class=\"feishu-columns-node\"><div data-block-id=\"localcolumnblock-401b6afd-c697-41ad-bac1-2c23555ba0c0\" id=\"localcolumnblock-401b6afd-c697-41ad-bac1-2c23555ba0c0\" data-width-ratio=\"50\" data-local-column=\"true\" class=\"feishu-columns-block__col-wrap\"><div class=\"feishu-columns-block__col\"><h3 data-block-id=\"heading-9f9485cd-089a-4cd4-bd8c-6afd6fc4f893\" id=\"heading-9f9485cd-089a-4cd4-bd8c-6afd6fc4f893\" data-heading-id=\"heading-9f9485cd-089a-4cd4-bd8c-6afd6fc4f893\">O (Opportunities) 机会</